"----------------------------------------------------------------------
" free key to bind
" 1. function keys: <F3>-<F12>
" 2. normal mode: <C-h>, <C-j>, <C-k>, <C-n>, <C-p>
" 3. insert mode: <C-b>
" 4. visual mode: <C-h>, <C-j>, <C-k>, <C-n>, <C-p>, <C-r>, <C-t>, Q
